{"tid":1818151,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我今年25  做緊自己嗰座嘅互助委員會成員 你問我答","createTime":"2020-01-09T16:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T17:51:42.000Z","uid":304634,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d3bdfe857897f8acb47c965444eb1577c825a78d","tid":1818151,"uid":304634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T16:07:43.000Z","msg":"唔該光復係要由自己屋企做起<br />\n<br />\n大部分互助委員會都係由一班師奶+阿叔組成<br />\n<br />\n主要都係傾下每一年去旅行去邊度<br />\n<br />\n但係其實係可以幫到當區區議員收風<br />\n因為開咗一個半鐘頭會就可以八到你個區<br />\n發生咩事<br />\n可以畀當區區議員一知道咗就即刻去做嘢<br />\n因為而家啲老嘢就算知道有嗰件事<br />\n都唔會主動去搵區議員<br />\n<br />\n而家成班藍絲每個星期圍爐 罵嗰黄絲區議員 做唔到嘢<br />\n<br />\n唔該後生嘅<br />\n真係幫手做下你屋企嗰座嘅互助委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(  workload 仲少過做學生會)"},{"pid":"1e2640814edb3921d08167cea1324f97349550eb","tid":1818151,"uid":304634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T16:09:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ceb1d7ed71a36f5ba9390755c438c215406c0ea7","tid":1818151,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T16:13:39.000Z","msg":"我個屋苑俾班保安公司 幫啲委員會種票<br />\n仲係到 諗緊點拆<br />\n<br />\n但真係好重要 大家try try <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73d37c1fc0e4f0f52e176ee3dffc1e624d6a825","tid":1818151,"uid":31174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T16:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a274253d2f936de36fe0f3501289f4917733d3","tid":1818151,"uid":304634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ceb1d7ed71a36f5ba9390755c438c215406c0ea7","tid":1818151,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T16:13:39.000Z","msg":"我個屋苑俾班保安公司 幫啲委員會種票<br />\n仲係到 諗緊點拆<br />\n<br />\n但真係好重要 大家try try <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hk